# Project File Locator [CRITICAL REFERENCE]

This rule provides a centralized index of important project files and their locations for quick reference. When files need to be located, consult this document first before performing extensive searches.

## Core Source Files

| Component           | Description                       | Primary File Location                            |
|---------------------|-----------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Plugin Bootstrap    | Main plugin file                  | `austin-shows-events/austin-shows-events.php`    |
| Theme Root          | Custom theme directory            | `austin-shows-theme/`                            |
| Plugin Includes     | PHP classes for plugin            | `austin-shows-events/includes/`                  |
| Theme Functions     | Main theme functions file         | `austin-shows-theme/functions.php`               |
| Docker Configuration| Docker environment definition     | `docker-compose.yml`                             |
| WP Env Configuration| WP Env specific settings        | `.wp-env.json`                                   |

## Important Configuration Files

| File Type           | Description                   | Location             |
|---------------------|-------------------------------|----------------------|
| PHPCS Configuration | PHP Code Sniffer config       | `phpcs.xml` or `phpcs.xml.dist` |
| Composer Config     | PHP dependencies              | `composer.json`      |
| NPM Config          | JavaScript dependencies       | `package.json`       |
| Behat Config        | Behat test suite config       | `behat.yml`          |
| PHPUnit Config      | PHPUnit test suite config     | `phpunit.xml.dist`   |
| Git Ignore          | Git ignore patterns           | `.gitignore`         |
| Environment Vars    | Environment variables         | `.env` / `.env.example`|

## Key Documentation Files

| Documentation Type  | Description                     | Location                         |
|---------------------|---------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Acceptance Report   | Latest test results             | `acceptance-criteria-report.md`  |
| User Story Root     | Top-level user story directory  | `docs/user-stories/`             |
| Technical Docs Root | Top-level technical docs        | `docs/technical/`                |
